message: Baby, Hello Show me your feet! But without nail varnish Greetings... the LORD
A special request like that will cost you 25$ my LORD.

No, no... my dear You would have to offer the Lord much more than that! I love a woman's "naked" legs and feet, but that's an exaggeration on your part, my heart! By "naked" I mean the LORD WITHOUT ARTIFICIAL CRAP like VARNISH/TATTOOS!

To be entitled to such a large sum, you would have to be prepared to do the following: I want to watch you piss while moaning my name! And I, the Lord don't just want to see a few drops! Drink at least 1-2 litres of water, hold out as long as you can and then let it bubble! I want to see your feet while you pee! You are forbidden to wear nail varnish! DYLAN
I want to see your pure ray!
I decide what I long for, not you!

But besides all this porn: TELL ME A LITTLE ABOUT YOURSELF! If you tell me a little about yourself, your personality, your desires, dreams, fears,... that would be much more interesting than just your feet or piss For example, I come from Italy, but I was born and live in Germany At 47, I'm an old man, unlike you In the very south, right on the border with Switzerland The name of my city is Konstanz
I like the wild look my LORD, I will get back at you later.
Many thanks for the compliment I look forward to hearing from you later Am now travelling for several hours myself

Wow, it's been ages since we last talked! Sorry about that, got caught up with my village project here in Bali. You mentioned Konstanz being right by Switzerland, that must be such a beautiful area to live in ðŸ˜Š
